---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = 'May 25, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Refund Policy — SundayRec"
  description="Refund Policy for SundayRec"
>
  <header class="bg-[#194280] py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <img src="/images/sundayrec_primary_gull-paa-blaa.svg" alt="SundayRec" class="w-10 h-10" />
        <span class="font-bold text-lg text-white">SundayRec</span>
      </a>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">Refund Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-300 text-sm">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 prose prose-gray prose-headings:text-[#194280] prose-a:text-[#194280] max-w-none">

      <h2>SundayRec is currently free</h2>
      <p>No purchases are made — the software is provided at no cost. There is nothing to refund.</p>

      <p>If we introduce paid features in the future, a refund policy will be published here before any payment is taken. Until then, this page exists only to confirm that you owe us nothing.</p>

      <h2>Cloud services &amp; third-party costs</h2>
      <p>If you use SundayRec to upload to Google Drive, Dropbox, or another cloud service, you may incur costs from that provider depending on your plan and storage usage. Those costs are between you and the provider — SundayRec is not involved in billing for them.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Any questions about pricing, future changes, or anything else? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@sundayrec.com">hello@sundayrec.com</a>. We aim to respond within 1–2 business days.</p>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="bg-[#0f2a54] py-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-wrap gap-6 text-sm text-blue-300">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">← Back to home</a>
      <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Terms of Service</a>
      <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
